OL,3,CMedics 'conditionally discharged'
OL,4,Cafter shortcomings in patient care
OL,6,FTwo Jersey medics who were found
OL,7,Fguilty of failing to adequately care
OL,8,Ffor a man in the moments before he
OL,9,Fdied have been sentenced at the
OL,10,Fisland's Royal Court.
OL,12,FParamedic John Sutherland, 61, and
OL,13,Fambulance technician Tom Le Sauteur,
OL,14,F36, were convicted in June on one
OL,15,Fcount each of breaching health and
OL,16,Fsafety law.
