OL,3,CMedics 'conditionally discharged'
OL,4,Cafter shortcomings in patient care
OL,6,FJurats decided that it was "not
OL,7,Fappropriate to impose a fine" and
OL,8,Finstead decided to give both men a
OL,9,Fconditional discharge for two years,
OL,10,Fwhich means they will be back in court
OL,11,Fif they commit any further offences.
OL,13,FSutherland and Le Sauteur have also
OL,14,Fbeen ordered to pay #500 each in court
OL,15,Fcosts.
OL,17,FThe case concerned patient Frazer
OL,18,FIrvine who died from a cardiac arrest
OL,19,Fin March 2022.
