OL,3,CMedics 'conditionally discharged'
OL,4,Cafter shortcomings in patient care
OL,6,FMr Irvine had called 999 for himself
OL,7,Fafter a suspected pill and alcohol
OL,8,Foverdose.
OL,10,FHis condition worsened after the
OL,11,Fambulance arrived and the prosecution
OL,12,Fargued that Sutherland and Le Sauteur
OL,13,Ffailed to put him in the recovery
OL,14,Fposition, did not recognise he was
OL,15,Fstruggling to breathe and failed to
OL,16,Fprovide adequate care during
OL,17,Fresuscitation.
