OL,3,CMedics 'conditionally discharged'
OL,4,Cafter shortcomings in patient care
OL,6,FBoth men have been suspended by their
OL,7,Femployer Jersey Ambulance Service
OL,8,Fsince 23 March 2022 pending the
OL,9,Foutcome of an internal investigation,
OL,10,Fdue to conclude in the coming weeks.
OL,12,FSutherland and Le Sauteur have told
OL,13,FITV News that they intend to appeal
OL,14,Ftheir sentence.
